VMCondor: generic Cloud Init user_data template file for use with Vacuum
based systems (Vac,Vcycle)

Just do  make  to build the user_data file from the component files

If you have experiment or VO-specific files, you can include them by
making files with names ending in ".write_files" containing Cloud
Config instructions for creating a file.

If you have experiment or VO-specific condor settings, you can include
them by making files with names ending in ".condor" 